  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align:center;\">1/<i>a</i> = 1/<i>b</i> &minus; 1/<i>c</i> &minus; 1/<i>d</i></p><p>The given equation relates the positive variables <i>a</i>, <i>b</i>, <i>c</i>, and <i>d</i>. Which of the following is equivalent to <i>b</i>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><i>a</i> + <i>c</i> + <i>d</i></p>"
    },
    {
